Add @cognac{60%ml}, @orange liqueur{30%ml}, @fresh lemon juice{15%ml} to a #cocktail shaker{} with ice and shake for ~{15%seconds}.

Doble strain over ice into a chilled (no ice) #nick & nora glass{} 

Garnish with an @orange peel{1}.

-- The recipe balance can be done in many ways and has been over
-- the years. You can also try a 2:1:1 balance or even a 3:2:2
-- ratio of strong to sweet/sour.
